items.title: SCQ, Gm3: VAN @ MIN
items.description: Extended highlights of the Vancouver Canucks at the Minnesota Wild

items.title: Recap: VAN 3, MIN 0
items.blurb: Canucks take 2-1 series lead with 3-0 win
items.description: Jacob Markstrom was perfect in net and Quinn Hughes assisted on goals for Brock Boeser, Antoine Roussel and Elias Pettersson in a 3-0 win

items.title: RR: WSH @ PHI
items.description: Extended highlights of the Washington Capitals at the Philadelphia Flyers

items.title: Recap: WSH 1, PHI 3
items.blurb: Flyers' 2nd line combines for eight points in 3-1 win
items.description: Scott Laughton, Kevin Hayes and Travis Konecny combined for eight points, leading the Flyers past the Capitals, 3-1, in Round Robin play

items.title: RR: VGK @ STL
items.description: Extended highlights of the Vegas Golden Knights at the St. Louis Blues

items.title: Recap: VGK 6, STL 4
items.blurb: Tuch, Theodore score twice in Golden Knights' 6-4 win
items.description: Alex Tuch and Shea Theodore each scored two goals, leading the Golden Knights past the Blues, 6-4, in a back-and-forth Round Robin game

items.title: SCQ, Gm3: TOR @ CBJ
items.blurb: SCQ, Gm3: Maple Leafs @ Blue Jackets
items.description: Extended highlights of the Toronto Maple Leafs at the Columbus Blue Jackets

items.title: Recap: TOR 3, CBJ 4 - F/OT
items.blurb: Dubois records hat trick, OT winner in Game 3
items.description: Pierre-Luc Dubois recorded a hat trick on the game-winning goal in overtime to lead the Blue Jackets to a 2-1 series lead

items.title: SCQ, Gm4: CGY @ WPG
items.description: Extended highlights of the Calgary Flames at the Winnipeg Jets

items.title: Recap: CGY 4, WPG 0
items.blurb: Talbot, Flames defeat Jets, win series
items.description: Cam Talbot made 31 saves in a 4-0 shutout victory against the Jets, helping the Flames win the series, 3-1

items.title: SCQ, Gm4: NYI @ FLA
items.description: Condensed Game: Extended highlights of the New York Islanders at the Florida Panthers

items.title: Recap: NYI 5, FLA 1
items.description: Mat Barzal and Anthony Beauvillier shined in the Islanders' 5-1 win against the Panthers, closing their Stanley Cup Qualifier series

items.title: SCQ, Gm4: NSH @ ARI
items.description: Condensed Game: Extended highlights of the Nashville Predators at the Arizona Coyotes

items.title: Recap: NSH 3, ARI 4
items.blurb: Coyotes win first playoff series since 2012
items.description: Brad Richardson stuffed in an overtime winner to lift the Coyotes over the Predators and send them to their first playoff series win since 2012

items.title: SCQ, Gm4: PIT @ MTL
items.description: Extended highlights of the Pittsburgh Penguins at the Montreal Canadiens

items.title: Recap: PIT 0, MTL 2
items.blurb: Lehkonen, Price help Canadiens earn series win
items.description: Artturi Lehkonen broke a scoreless tie late in the 3rd, and Carey Price made 22 saves as the Canadiens topped the Penguins, 2-0, to advance
